  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note-inn-services",
      "title": "Inn Services & Prices",
      "category": "settlement",
      "content": "**The Rusty Dragon**\nA modest two-story inn with comfortable lodgings and hearty meals.\n\n**Ground Floor**:\n- Common Room (40ft × 30ft) - Fireplace, tables, chairs\n- Bar - Ale, wine, spirits\n- Kitchen - Hot meals prepared daily\n- Storage\n\n**Second Floor**:\n- 7 Guest Rooms (each 20ft × 20ft)\n- Central Hallway\n\n**Typical Prices** (per SRD Lifestyle Expenses):\n- Common Room Bed: 5 sp/night\n- Private Room: 5 gp/night\n- Meals: 3 sp (modest) to 8 sp (comfortable)\n- Ale/Beer: 4 cp/mug\n- Wine (common): 2 sp/pitcher\n- Wine (fine): 10 gp/bottle\n\n**Building Properties**:\n- **Material**: Wood\n- **AC**: 15\n- **HP**: ~300 (large wooden structure)\n- **Floors**: 2 (ground + second)\n- **Features**: Fireplace, bar, kitchen, 7 guest rooms",
      "position": {"viewLevel": "adventure", "x": 120, "y": 60},
